Dynamic Hotel Revenue Dashboard
Overview
Welcome to the Dynamic Hotel Revenue Dashboard repository! This project aims to provide a comprehensive and interactive dashboard monitoring the revenue figures of a residential hotel.
The dashboard includes key performance indicators (KPIs) commonly used in the hospitality industry to track growth and revenue generation.

Features
Dynamic Visualizations: The dashboard incorporates various dynamic visualizations to give users a clear understanding of the hotel's revenue performance.
Filtering Options: Users can filter data based on cities and room types, allowing for a more detailed analysis and comparison.
Key Performance Indicators (KPIs): The dashboard includes essential KPIs to help stakeholders make informed decisions about the hotel's financial health.

The room analysis.pdf consists of the dashboard. Please open the file in Microsoft Power BI to test the dashboard by yourselves.

